snippet.textDisplay: So happy  to see that one of the best  singers of our country  has sung along with some of the best musicians the world. Sayad iss liye hum India ke log jab dhuki hote hai tab Coke Studio Pakistan dekhte hai. The only musicial platform which is trying to preserve the song of the soul and soil. Iske liye Coke Studioyon ke production team aur waha ke musicians  ki jitni bhi taarife ki jai utni kam hai. Ek hi Dil hai jo har baar Coke Studio Pakistan ka koi naya season jeet ke chala jata hai. Respect from India for keeping alive the songs and melodies of the soil
